    dc:description "FIGURES 56A–H. Hexapopha izquierdoi sp. nov., female (MPEG 37807; PBI_OON 45749). A–B habitus. A dorsal view. B lateral view. C–E carapace. C dorsal view. D ventral view. E anterior view. F abdomen, ventral view. G–H epigastric region. G ventral view (arrow: margin of postepigastric plate). H dorsal view. Scale bars: 0.1mm." ;
